The psycho who killed Cindy and Fanny?

290
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,679
Did you get a clear look at them?

291
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:51,720
Sis Siqi,

292
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:53,519
do you remember the Bai family's painting?

293
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,919
I had a dream.

294
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:57,519
I dreamed of a man dressed in white.

295
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,320
He said he was the second son of the Bai family.

296
00:10:59,879 --> 00:11:01,120
He wanted to find a woman to marry.

297
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:03,639
But I was too ugly.

298
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,840
He didn't want me.

299
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:07,240
I never believed in monsters and demons,

300
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:08,919
but I think...

301
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,879
Should we just call the police first?

302
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,279
There are police up ahead.

303
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,960
I know you've always wanted to steal

304
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,440
what's in Boss Bai's safe.

305
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,480
If you don't want her to find out,

306
00:11:21,279 --> 00:11:22,399
just drive through!

307
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:24,919
Stop the car!

308
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,360
Stop the car!

309
00:11:27,279 --> 00:11:28,080
Hurry, after them!

